title: High acupuncture expectancy is associated with shorter time to ovulation and higher chances of ovulation in infertile patients with PCOS receiving acupuncture: a secondary analysis of a randomized controlled trial.
abstract: To investigate the influence of acupuncture expectancy on fertility outcomes in infertile women with polycystic ovary syndrome (PCOS) receiving active or control acupuncture with or without clomiphene.
journal: Acupuncture in medicine : journal of the British Medical Acupuncture Society
